title: Fairy dust and magic at Murchison PS
media: https://s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/wp-media-lib/wnews/gallery/2021/07/Roy was excited to see the new fairy house.jpg
abstract: Murchison Primary School students were thrilled to return from holidays to find that a team of hard-working fairies had moved in and created a whole fairy village at the school!
